## Third-party trademarks

Third-party brand marks are used nominatively only — through a user-selected branded variant or
explicit icon on the user's own diagram — and never in ThreatForge branding or as a component
type's default glyph. Geometry ships unmodified from the pinned Simple Icons release. The block
below lists marks whose artwork currently ships, with the owner and trademark-policy URL for each
so a takedown can be honored mechanically. `aws` (the `amazonwebservices` mark) is absent from the
pinned release and ships an abstract fallback glyph, so it is not listed here.

